Package: geoManipulatoR
Type: Package
Title: Geographic Lookups and IMD Aggregation Utilities
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Slater", email = "dslater629@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for geographic data manipulation and deprivation analysis.
    Provides utilities to aggregate Index of Multiple Deprivation (IMD) scores
    from LSOA level to higher geographies using population weighting, calculate
    national ranks and deciles, and download postcode-level lookups from the
    ONS Postcode Directory with optional enrichment of higher geographies and
    IMD attributes.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    rlang,
    stringdist,
    httr,
    jsonlite
